HEADWORD: Postexist
<hw>Post`ex*ist"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>post-</ets> + <ets>exist</ets>.]</ety> <def>To exist after; to live
